tafsir[22]{c,v,t}:
  38,62,"Bewﾉ兎 townitiiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n wi'a: Ko haﾉ擁 men yi'ugol ka Yiite gaa, worﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 men limtaynoo ka aduna, jeyaaﾉ兎 e bomﾉ兎, hannduﾉ兎 e lepte?"
  38,63,"Hara men falju e kon men jagitornoo ﾉ兎 kon jalnori, tawa ﾉ兎 handaa e lepte, kaa hara ﾉ兎 naatu Yiite, gite amen yawti ﾉ兎?"
  38,64,"Pellet, ko Men jantanii on kon, e ko yedduﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n wenjorndirta hakkunde maﾉ橡兎 ﾃ疎lnde Darngal, ko goonga mo sikke alaa e mu'un."
  38,65,"An Muhammadu, maakan yimﾉ兎 maa yedduﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n: Anndee ko mi jertinoowo on, e lepte Allah ﾉ容n, fii wata ﾉ容 yanir e mon, sabu yeddugol mon fenna Nulaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n. Anndo kadi, alaa reweteeﾉ熔 hannduﾉ熔 e dewal, si wanaa Allah Seniiﾉ熔 On. Ko Kanko woni Bajjo ka mawngu e sifaaji e ka inﾉ容 Mun, Fooluﾉ熔 kala huunde. Mo huunde kala yankinii ﾆ隔m."
  38,66,"Ko Kanko woni Jeyﾉ熔 kammuuli ﾉ擁n, e leydi ndin, e kon ko woni hakkunde majji. Fooluﾉ熔 e laamu Mun, Mo gooto foolataa. Haforoowo junuubi jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko tuubuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  38,67,"An Nulaaﾉ熔, maakan ﾉ兎e fennooﾉ兎 : ndee Alqur'aanaare, ko kumpital mawngal fiyaaku."
  38,68,"Kono hiﾉ熔n ﾉ蓉urnii e on kabaaru mawnuﾉ熔 fiyaaku. On alaa yeﾆｴﾆｴitaade e makko."
  38,69,"Mi heﾉ殿taano ganndal, e ko feﾆｴﾆｴaynoo hakkunde Malaa'ika'en, fii tagugol Aadama, si wanaano Allah wahayini ﾉ蓉m e am, O anndimmi."
  38,70,"Allah wahayiniraali e am, si wanaa tawde ko mi jertinoowo on, e lepte Makko ﾉ容n, ﾉ殿nninano on."
  38,71,"Janto nde Joomi maa daalannoo Malaa'ika'en: Min ko Mi tagiroowo ﾉ殿nndinke, woni Aadama (yo o his) immorde e loopal."
  38,72,"Si Mi fotindirii tagu makko ngun, Mi moﾆｴﾆｴintinii mbaadi makko ndin, mi wuttii ruuhu Am on e makko, ko yo on sujjan mo."
  38,73,"Malaa'ika'en ﾉ熔ftii yamaruyee Joomi maﾉ橡兎 on, ﾉ兎 sujji ﾉ兎 denndaangal, sujuudu teddungal. Alaa mo sujjanaano Aadama e maﾉ橡兎."
  38,74,"Si wanaa Ibuliisa, o mawnitinii sujjugol ngol, o woni jeyaaﾉ熔 e yedduﾉ兎 Joomi mun."
  38,75,"Allah daali: Ko an yo Ibuliisa, ko honﾉ蓉m haﾉ蓉 maa sujjangol Aadama, mo tagirmi juuﾉ容 Am? Ko mawnintinaare haﾉ蓉 maa kaa hari nun ko a jeyanooﾉ熔 e townitaniiﾉ兎 Joomi mun ﾉ兎n?"
  38,76,"Ibuliisa wi'i: Ko min ﾉ砥ri Aadama moﾆｴﾆｴude. Tawde A tagirii lam immorde e yiite, A tagirii mo kanko e loopal. Sikkugol mo wonnde yiite ﾉ砥ri loope teddude."
  38,77,"Alla daalani ibuliisa: Yaltu ka Aljanna ton, sabu ko a huﾉ預aﾉ熔 Kiitaaﾉ預."
  38,78,"Pellet, raﾉ容ede ka Aljanna fawike ma, haa ﾃ疎laande nﾉ屠odi kuuﾉ容, nden woni ﾃ疎lnde Darngal."
  38,79,"Ibuliisa wi'i: Nennitanam maayugol, haa ﾃｱalnde immintaa jeyaaﾉ兎 Maa ﾉ兎n."
  38,80,"Allah daali: A jeyaama e nennitanaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  38,81,"A nennitanaama, haa e happu anndaaﾉ熔, halkeede ma."
  38,82,"Ibuliisa wi'i: Mi woondirii kattal e mawngu Maa ngun ! Ma mi majjin ﾉ妬ﾉ遼兎 Aadama ﾉ兎n fow."
  38,83,"Si wanaa ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 daﾉ溶du-ﾆ蛎a bone am, heertinir-ﾆ蛎a ﾉ兎 e rewugol Am tun."